  "title": "ASSOCIATE",
  "description": "<p>You will be handling administrative tasks and providing support to other team members. This role is crucial for ensuring the smooth operation.</p><p>You will also provide other administrative support such as prepare invoicing, sales quotation, maintenance of copier machine, printing and filing of documents.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>1. To provide administrative support involving in document creation, editing, and production in support of the company's business operations.</p><p>2. Handling administrative support such as prepare invoicing, sales quotation, maintenance\nof copier machine, printing and filing of documents.</p><p>3. Ensure close monitoring and follow up for efficient accomplishment of tasks with deadlines.</p><p>4. Provide administrative support to other team members, such as filing, scheduling meetings, and preparing documents.</p><p>5. Handle company Account Payable (AP) and Account Receivable (AR).</p><p>6. Maintain a clean and organized work environment.</p><p>7. Perform other administrative duties as assigned.</p>",
